      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Main Flow\n\n1. Run pytest through `utils/configure_ci_otel.py`\n2. Copy the `trace_id` from the `OTEL TRACE START` or `OTEL TRACE END` log line\n3. Open Grafana Explore and select the `Jaeger` data source\n4. Use the `TraceID` query type to paste the trace ID directly\n\nUse Jaeger UI when you want the raw upstream interface, but Grafana is the intended main UI for trace lookup and navigation.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Using The UI",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Search Hints\n\nThe wrapper attaches CI and local metadata as resource attributes and Jaeger tags.\n\nUseful filters:\n\n- `service = transformers-pytest-demo`\n- `transformers.test.job = grafana_demo`\n- `transformers.test.job.id = ...`\n- `vcs.change.id = ...` in CI\n\nFor local runs, `deployment.environment=local` is also attached.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Search Filters",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Current Demo Settings\n\n- Collector endpoint: `http://localhost:5317`\n- Grafana: `http://localhost:3000`\n- Jaeger: `http://localhost:16687`\n- Recommended service name: `transformers-pytest-demo`\n- Recommended job name: `grafana_demo`\n\nThe slow-test table is now based on average duration across all fetched traces in the exporter lookback window.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Demo Configuration",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "inspect": false
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green"
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 14,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "countRows": false,
          "fields": "",
          "reducer": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "show": false
        },
        "showHeader": true
